data.description: Best Location!!  4 bdrm 3 bath mid century pool house has a master bedroom and bath suite and a private  gated side entrance to a charming bedroom/living area with a bath and small kitchen. All areas are attached but can be separated for privacy and short or long term rental. The spacious back yard has sparkling pool with mature citrus and olive trees completely enclosed by a block wall. Three sets of sliding glass doors lead out to this oasis adding serene views to all sections of the house. The front yard also has mature olive and mesquite trees as well as date palms with partial block wall ensuring more privacy. The garage has built in shelves for storage. Double windows throughout block noise and insulates for comfortable internal temperature and provide majestic mountain views from the front. Real brick wall adds to the uniqueness of the facade of this property. One of the lowest per square foot price available in this sought-after neighborhood. Don't miss out on this one!! Check out photos for floor plan and sq. feet.
